1. *Očekivala* je da će joj se on javiti nakon godinu dana. (She was expecting that he would get in touch with her after a year.)

2. *Očekivao* je da će se ona iznenada pojaviti. (He was expecting that she would suddenly appear.)

3. *Očekuju* se veliki promeni u naredne tri godine. (Big changes are expected in the next three years.)

4. Ona je *očekivala* da će dobiti bolji odgovor. (She was expecting to get a better answer.)

5. *Očekuje* se da će se situacija promeniti do petka. (It is expected that the situation will change by Friday.)